OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy this morning with
OL,6,Fthe chance of a few showers. Then dry
OL,7,Fthis afternoon with some sunshine
OL,8,Fbreaking through. Breezy along the
OL,9,Feast coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome sunshine. Then the rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will be dry with lengthy clear
OL,14,Fperiods. Chance of a ground frost in
OL,15,Fsheltered glens.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,18,Fday with plenty of sunshine, some high
OL,19,Fcloud in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
